of Coahuila state; and in Las Delicias, in neighboring Chihuahua
state, according to the statement.
   Federal agents also confiscated three pistols, one rifle, two
trucks, and 13 drums of jet fuel, the prosecutors said.
   There were no immediate details about any charges against the
suspects or the value of the confiscated drugs.
