   Stock prices eased today, weakened by investors
squeezing some profits out of a market that has been rising solidly
since late March.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrial stocks was down 5.14
points to 2,397.54 by 3 p.m. EDT.
   Among broader market indicators, the New York Stock Exchange
